Hotel Vintage Park is centrally located in downtown Seattle, it was very easy to get to the shopping areas/Pike Place Market and a few good restaurants.	Location was terrific (7 short blocks from Pike Place Market, and a similar distance to Westlake Center, gateway to the Seattle Center monorail).	Hotel Vintage Park was very quiet, in an excellent location, and the room was spectacular.	Good staff and service and in a good location for downtown Seattle.	The hotel and rooms are gorgeous, and the location is perfect--downtown but on a fairly quiet street.	This hotel is located right in the middle of downtown Seattle and is only a few blocks away from all the great eateries/bars/restaurants/pubs, etc.